3E%2C%20who%20plays%20Ellie%2C%20a%20scene%20in%20episode%20three%20was%20the%20hardest%20to%20shoot.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20season%20is%20based%20on%20the%202020%20game%20%26quot%3BThe%20Last%20of%20Us%20Part%20II%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20sparked%20controversy%20because%20of%20Joel's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20only%20a%20few%20minor%20differences%20between%20how%20Abby%20(Kaitlyn%20Dever)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-last-of-us-season-2-joel-death-explained-game-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekills%20Joel%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20series%20versus%20the%20game.%20It's%20a%20traumatic%20moment%20for%20Ellie%2C%20who%20is%20forced%20to%20watch%20Joel%20die.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20episode%20three%2C%20Ellie%20goes%20to%20Joel's%20house%20and%20smells%20one%20of%20the%20jackets%20in%20his%20closet%20as%20she%20grieves%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20adopted%20father%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%20God%2C%20in%20the%20closet%2C%20that%20was%20the%20hardest%20%5Bscene%5D.%20So%20I%20really%20struggle%20with%20crying%20in%20scenes.%20I%20can%20get%20a%20tear%20out%2C%20but%20that's%20different%20to%20crying.%20And%20even%20getting%20the%20tear%2C%20it%20doesn't%20come%20easy%20for%20me.%20I%20don't%20cry%20in%20front%20of%20people%20in%20my%20everyday%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramsey%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Ftv%2Ftv-news%2Fthe-last-of-us-bella-ramsey-toughest-scene-1236199152%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20published%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20very%2C%20very%20limited%20amount%20of%20people%20in%20my%20life%20will%20see%20me%20cry.%20And%20so%20having%20to%20do%20that%20on%20a%20set%20full%20of%20people%20with%20the%20monitor%20and%20then%20more%20people%20watching%20the%20monitors%E2%80%A6%20it's%20virtually%20impossible%20for%20me.%20So%20I%20was%20really%20worried%20about%20that%20scene%2C%20and%20that%20was%20the%20toughest%20one%20for%20me%20to%20shoot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamsey%20said%20to%20achieve%20the%20desired%20effect%2C%20they%20didn't%20recall%20sad%20memories%20but%20filming%20with%20Pedro%20Pascal%20instead.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222610%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20with%20long%20swept-back%20gray%20and%20brown%20hair%20stares%20at%20something%20on%20the%20ground.%20He%20has%20a%20gray%20mustache%20and%20a%20gray%20beard.%20He's%20wearing%20a%20thick%20black%20winter%20coat%20with%20a%20fur%20hood%20and%20a%20scarf.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d01482585f1dff88b1bc5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221596%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPedro%20Pascal%20as%20Joel%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Last%20of%20Us%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3Cp%3ELiane%20Hentscher%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20remembering%20us%20the%20first%20few%20times%20that%20we%20met%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20of%20shooting%20season%20one%20together%2C%20and%20the%20funniest%20moments.%20I%20was%20remembering%20all%20of%20that%20and%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20losing%20him%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20Joel%20and%20Ellie%2C%20but%20like%20me%20and%20Pedro%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20memories%20of%20me%20and%20Pedro%20and%20Joel%20and%20Ellie%20are%20so%20intertwined%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPascal%20previously%20touched%20on%20what%20it%20was%20like%20filming%20his%20brutal%20death%20scene%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Last%20of%20Us%26quot%3B%20season%20two%20when%20speaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Few.com%2Fthe-last-of-us-season-2-pedro-pascal-shocker-kaitlyn-dever-bella-ramsey-on-set-exclusive-11717893%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEntertainment%20Weekly%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20April%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20experienced%20anything%20like%20I%20did%20that%20day%20