%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20things%20entrepreneurs%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20when%20starting%20a%20company%2C%20according%20to%20two%20VC%20founders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CIV%20founders%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680c0ea43fe8d39283642a8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECIV%20cofounder%2C%20CEO%2C%20and%20managing%20partner%20(left)%20next%20to%20cofounders%20and%20managing%20partners%20Jeff%20Rosenthal%20(center)%20and%20Abhijoy%20Mitra%20(right).%3Cp%3ECIV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVC%20founders%20Jeff%20Rosenthal%20and%20Abhijoy%20Mitra%20share%20with%20BI%20the%20lessons%20they%20learned%20as%20investors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20aiming%20for%20capital%20efficiency%20and%20a%20large%20market%20is%20key%20to%20building%20a%20profitable%20product.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChoosing%20the%20right%20partner%20and%20hiring%20strong%20talent%20are%20also%20crucial%20for%20success%2C%20Rosenthal%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20cofounders%20of%20venture%20capital%20firm%20CIV%2C%20Jeff%20Rosenthal%20and%20Abhijoy%20Mitra%20have%20overseen%20the%20development%20of%20various%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20not%20100%20outlier%20founders%20and%20companies%20every%20year%20to%20bet%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20dozen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECIV%20has%20invested%20in%20companies%20like%20The%20Nuclear%20Company%20and%20Verse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20VCs%2C%20the%20goal%20of%20investing%20in%20a%20company%20is%20to%20see%20it%20go%20public%20and%20generate%20a%20return%20eventually.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fventure-capital-downturn-exodus-rethinking-career-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexit%20opportunities%20have%20become%20increasingly%20scarce%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20though%2C%20firms%20are%20raising%20the%20standards%20for%20evaluating%20which%20companies%20will%20make%20it%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20watching%20a%20number%20of%20failures%20and%20successes%2C%20these%20are%20the%20five%20key%20lessons%20the%20investors%20recommend%20to%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2a6fdeb-605b-4d40-8571-05a769d34242%5C%22%3E1.%20Be%20'laser-focused'%20on%20capital%20efficiency%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMitra%2C%20who%20has%20built%20his%20career%20investing%20in%20technology%2C%20said%20businesses%20in%20the%20industrial%20sector%20often%20fail%20because%20they%20don't%20transition%20from%20equity%20to%20non-equity%20funding%20quickly%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20infinite%20venture%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitra%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20be%20very%20efficient%20on%20dollars%20you%20raise%2C%20and%20really%20focus%20on%20building%20a%20profitable%20product%20in%20a%20well-defined%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20building%20real-world%20solutions%20and%20not%20over-relying%20on%20equity%20funding%20is%20crucial.%20Founders%20who%20build%20their%20companies%20with%20customers%20in%20mind%20will%20likely%20be%20more%20successful%20than%20those%20who%20build%20for%20investors%2C%20Mitra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20probably%20need%20half%20a%20billion%20of%20revenue%20and%20maybe%20the%20profitability%20to%20actually%20go%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitra%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20as%20a%20venture%20investor%2C%20we%20think%20about%20that%20constantly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f62543cf-c0cf-4f24-9c2b-29ccc10b87e8%5C%22%3E2.%20Build%20a%20product%20with%20a%20large%20target%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERosenthal%20said%20that%20often%20he%20sees%20highly%20talented%20people%20%26quot%3Bpick%20too%20small%20of%20a%20market.%26quot%3B%20Or%2C%20he%20said%20their%20%26quot%3Bangle%20of%20attack%26quot%3B%20into%20that%20market%20doesn't%20capture%20the%20scale%20needed%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20large%20business.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20scale%20and%20impact%20are%20%26quot%3Bmutually%20inclusive%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20game%20we're%20all%20trying%20to%20play%20is%20like%2C%20how%20do%20you%20really%20have%20impact%20in%20this%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20serial%20entrepreneur%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20taking%20the%20world%20where%20it%20is%2C%20versus%20where%20you%20want%20it%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitra%20said%20he's%20seen%20companies%20build%20a%20perfect%20product%20for%20a%20market%20that%20isn't%20quite%20ready%20for%20it%20too%20many%20times.%20While%20the%20founders%20and%20the%20products%20may%20be%20amazing%2C%20the%20target%20market%20has%20to%20have%20a%20real%20use%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20gotta%2C%20like%2C%20actually%20build%20something%20that%20is%20audacious%20and%20transformational%20for%20a%20big%20end%20market%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Mitra%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20that%20often%20means%20several%20billions%20of%20market%20cap%20to%20be%20accrued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbd7d104-da0a-4e77-ad0f-9671fef7f99d%5C%22%3E3.%20Choose%20the%20right%20partner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERosenthal%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bbreakup%20risk%20between%20partners%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20concerns%20institutional%20investors%20raise%20with%20companies.%20He%20said%20he%20pays%20close%20attention%20to%20cofounders%20and%20how%20they%20interact%20with%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%2C%20how%20do%20you%20guys%20know%20each%20other%3F%20How%20close%20of%20friends%20are%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenthal%2C%20who%20partnered%20with%20his%20best%20friend%20and%20colleague%20to%20form%20CIV%2C%20said%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bwrote%20each%20other%20back%20and%20forth%20like%20pen%20pals%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20were%20on%20the%20same%20page%20before%20partnering.%20He%20said%20they%20would%20ask%20each%20other%20questions%20about%20what%20they%20envisioned%20for%20their%20business%20culture%2C%20or%20when%20they%20planned%20to%20start%20and%20end%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenthal%20also%20suggests%20talking%20to%20a%20potential%20partner's%20former%20employees%20and%20friends%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20other%20person%20operates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20worth%20doing%20the%20extra%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20it%20secretly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5119914-0154-4cb0-a913-5478971b86bf%5C%22%3E4.%20Talent%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERosenthal%20said%20that%20hiring%20the%20right%20talent%20is%20key%20when%20starting%20a%20business.%20If%20you%20can%20recruit%20the%20top%20talent%2C%20you%20have%20a%20comparative%20advantage%20that's%20measurable%2C%20Rosenthal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20hire%20strong%20talent%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20replicate%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20said.%20That%20doesn't%20always%20mean%20the%20company%20ends%20up%20in%20the%20right%20place%2C%20but%20it%20can%20define%20its%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20consistently%20reminded%20that%20the%20success%20or%20failure%20of%20these%20enterprises%20often%20starts%20with%20like%2C%20the%20first%20four%20to%20six%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c69121c1-1e5b-4b03-8578-51358841815f%5C%22%3E5.%20Have%20a%20'durable%20strategy'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERosenthal%20said%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20founders%20have%20a%20thesis%20but%20end%20up%20reacting%20to%20whatever%20happens%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20building-the-plane-while-you're-flying-it%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hate%20that%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenthal%20said%20that's%20how%20he%20operated%20when%20he%20was%2023.%20At%2040%2C%20though%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20measure%2020%20times%20and%20cut%20just%20once.%20While%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20may%20have%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20founders%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20accomplish%20that%20vision%2C%20Rosenthal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20really%20have%20a%20durable%20strategy%2C%20not%20just%20a%20thesis%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenthal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitra%20said%20that%20even%20if%20things%20are%20going%20well%2C%20businesses%20will%20inevitably%20have%20to%20experience%20downturns%2C%20whether%20from%20geopolitical%20issues%20or%20other%20challenges.%20Sometimes%2C%20he%20said%2C%20you%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bmiss%20the%20hype%20and%20sit%20something%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20it's%20not%20the%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-founders-share-5-things-to-consider-when-starting-company-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745837162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680c0e8ba466d2b74ab44288%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-founders-share-5-things-to-consider-when-starting-company-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CIV%20founders%20Jeff%20Rosenthal%20and%20Abhijoy%20Mitra%20have%20overseen%20the%20successes%20and%20failures%20of%20various%20companies%20in%20tech%20sectors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-founders-share-5-things-to-consider-when-starting-company-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parcel%20giant%20DHL%20says%20it%20can%20deliver%20packages%20worth%20more%20than%20%24800%20to%20American%20customers%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3