y%20returning%20to%20school%20with%20a%20renewed%20sense%20of%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20started%20watching%20her%20peers%20go%20on%20and%20graduate%20and%20move%20on%2C%20and%20she%20was%20working%20as%20a%20waitress%2C%20and%20she%20was%20like%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20I%20want%20to%20get%20back%20into%20this.%20I%20think%20I'm%20losing%20time%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20she%20went%20back%20to%20school%2C%20she%20knew%20what%20she%20was%20going%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20to%20college%20straight%20away%20can%20still%20be%20a%20great%20decision%2C%20he%20said.%20People%20who%20know%20exactly%20what%20they're%20interested%20in%20dive%20into%20higher%20education%20with%20a%20unique%20tenacity%2C%20Savage%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20I've%20ever%20met%20who%20went%20back%20to%20school%20knowing%20what%20they%20were%20going%20for%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20them%20ever%20got%20anything%20but%20an%20A%20in%20anything%20that%20they%20were%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20when%20you're%20interested%20in%20your%20subject%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20really%20well%20at%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20individual%20choices%20someone%20makes%2C%20Savage%20believes%20there%20might%20be%20a%20bit%20too%20much%20dependence%20on%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20kinds%20of%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20enough%20recognition%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bmental%20frames%26quot%3B%20that%20people%20can%20bring%20to%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20long%20said%20that%20there%20are%20people%20I%20have%20met%2C%20who%20don't%20make%20stuff%20for%20a%20living%2C%20who%20I%20would%20hire%20in%20a%20heartbeat%20to%20build%20stuff%20in%20this%20cave%2C%20on%20the%20clock%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Savage%20said%20from%20his%20workshop.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20I%20just%20know%20their%20skill.%20I%20can%20see%20it%20in%20them.%26quot%3B%3