ferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-explained-mckinsey-bain-bcg-compare-big-three-strategy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMBB%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20and%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group.%20And%20then%20there%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-consultancies-leaders-pwc-deloitte-ey-kpmg-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20PwC%2C%20Deloitte%2C%20KPMG%2C%20and%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20a%20new%20wave%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eupstarts%20fueled%20by%20AI%20is%20attempting%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20that%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20these%20new%20firms%20come%20from%20the%20traditional%20consulting%20realm.%20They%20told%20Business%20Insider%20their%20experiences%20not%20only%20give%20them%20marketable%20skills%20but%20have%20also%20helped%20them%20identify%20new%20opportunities%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20boutique%20firms.%20They%20are%20much%20smaller%20than%20the%20established%20ones%2C%20often%20run%20by%20teams%20ranging%20from%20just%20a%20few%20people%20to%20a%20few%20hundred.%20They're%20also%20more%20specialized%2C%20focusing%20on%20areas%20like%20pricing%20strategy%2C%20cost%20reduction%2C%20or%20refining%20slide%20decks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20importantly%2C%20they%20are%20all%20in%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20said%20their%20methods%20have%20helped%20them%20reduce%20old-school%20bureaucracy%2C%20offer%20more%20competitive%20rates%2C%20and%20make%20the%20human%20side%20of%20consulting%20work%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20eight%20boutique%20firms%20that%20are%2C%20to%20varying%20degrees%2C%20challenging%20the%20classic%20consulting%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22575607dc-c159-497c-83d1-8d5c108f45bf%5C%22%3EXavier%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xavier.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXavier%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edescribes%20itself%20as%20the%20world's%20first%20AI%20strategy%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Joao%20Filipe%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Xavier%20and%20a%20former%20McKinsey%20consultant%2C%20the%20Xavier%20AI%20chatbot%20can%20provide%20clear%2C%20actionable%20business%20knowledge%20and%20deliverables%2C%20like%20a%2060-page%20business%20plan%2C%20a%20sales%20presentation%2C%20or%20a%20detailed%20marketing%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilipe%20said%20Xavier%20AI%20has%20its%20own%20proprietary%20reasoning%20engine%20that%20is%20tailor-made%20for%20business%20use%20cases%20and%20can%20provide%20detailed%20sources%20without%20the%20hallucination%20you%20might%20find%20with%20other%20chatbots.%20He%20said%20Xavier%20can%20provide%20both%20strategy%20recommendations%20and%20actionable%20plans%20for%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B99.9%25%20of%20businesses%20could%20really%20never%20afford%20McKinsey%20or%20any%20of%20the%20MBBs%2C%26quot%3B%20Filipe%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20created%20Xavier%20AI%20so%20that%20anyone%20could%20have%20the%20power%20of%20a%20consulting%20firm%20at%20their%20hands%20when%20they%20need%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXavier%20AI%20just%20launched%2C%20but%20Filipe%20said%20he's%20been%20piloting%20it%20with%20different%20clients%2C%20including%20an%20international%20bank%20using%20it%20to%20research%20potential%20clients%20and%20better%20understand%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c97545db-e4e8-4ab2-80da-e543f339beba%5C%22%3EPerceptis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlibek%20Dostiyarov%2C%20a%20former%20McKinsey%20consultant%2C%20and%20Yersultan%20Sapar%2C%20a%20former%20engineer%20at%20Apple%2C%20cofounded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperceptis-ai-consulting-startup-cofounders-mckinsey-apple-write-proposals-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerceptis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20aims%20to%20help%20smaller%20and%20midsize%20firms%20compete%20with%20bigger%20industry%20players%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20streamline%20some%20of%20the%20more%20tedious%20processes%20in%20consulting%2C%20like%20proposal%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptis%20is%20now%20focused%20on%20the%20business%20development%20side%20of%20consulting.%20Its%20AI-powered%20operating%20system%20can%20do%20industry%20research%2C%20identify%20opportunities%20that%20align%20with%20their%20client's%20skillset%20and%20background%2C%20and%20create%20detailed%2C%20custom%20proposals%20that%20the%20client%20can%20use%20to%20win%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDostiyarov%20told%20BI%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20internal%20processes%20completed%20at%20consulting%20firms%20are%20heavy%20with%20manual%20labor%20and%20%26quot%3Blend%20themselves%20almost%20perfectly%20to%20what%20GenAI%20is%20capable%20of%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20Perceptis%20could%20make%20smaller%20firms%2C%20which%20don't%20typically%20have%20internal%20AI%20tools%2C%20more%20competitive%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20told%20BI%20this%20week%20that%20while%20initially%20serving%20boutique%20management%20consultancies%2C%20it's%20now%20quickly%20expanding%20to%20serve%20IT%20services%2C%20system%20integrators%2C%20software%20developers%2C%20financial%20services%2C%20design%20firms%2C%20and%20real%20estate%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptis%20had%20raised%20%243.6%20million%20in%20funding%20as%20of%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22441b350f-5cb1-4111-a0a6-f4a9920fd1ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESIB%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESIB%20specializes%20in%20helping%20clients%20like%20restaurant%20groups%2C%20hospitals%2C%20universities%2C%20and%20government%20agencies%20find%20savings%20in%20fixed%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20expenses%20that%20remain%20static%20regardless%20of%20how%20much%20a%20company%20produces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESIB%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-work-silicon-vallery-grind-culture-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShannon%20Copeland%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20BI%20that%20these%20are%20often%20found%20in%20areas%20that%20%26quot%3Bescape%20scrutiny%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20fees%20for%20telecommunications%2C%20utilities%2C%20waste%20removal%2C%20shipping%2C%20and%20software%20licenses.%20According%20to%C2%A0his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20Copeland%20is%20an%20alum%20of%20Accenture%20and%20Deloitte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESIB%20has%20grown%20since%20its%202008%20launch%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina.%20It's%20now%20a%20national%20firm%20serving%20hundreds%20of%20clients%2C%20ranging%20from%20Kroger%20and%20Marriott%20to%20governments%20like%20San%20Diego%20County.%20It%20recently%20added%20over%20a%20dozen%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20and%20private%20equity%20firms.%20Since%20its%20launch%2C%20SIB%C2%A0says%20it%C2%A0has%20identified%20more%20than%20%248%20billion%20in%20cost%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECopeland%20said%20that%2C%20unlike%20traditional%20consulting%20firms%2C%20SIB%20operates%20under%20a%20contingency%20model.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20find%20savings%2C%20we%20don't%20get%20paid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20firm%20doesn't%20charge%20fees%20upfront.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESIB%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Euses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-an-ai-agent-depends-who-you-ask-2025-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAgents%2520are%2520commonly%2520defined%2520as%2Cbeing%2520prompted%2520by%2520a%2520user.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20monitor%20invoices%2C%20vendor%20contracts%2C%20and%20billing%20patterns.%20The%20firm's%20consultants%20use%20the%20resulting%20insights%20to%20negotiate%20better%20contract%20terms%20or%20restructure%20their%20vendor%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20think%20of%20us%20as%20part%20AI%2C%20part%20old-school%20operator%2C%26quot%3B%20Copeland%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20cost-cutting%2C%20the%20firm%20also%20focuses%20on%20strengthening%20relationships%2C%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20traditional%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20actually%20encourage%20vendors%20and%20clients%20to%20return%20to%20high-trust%2C%20high-accountability%20partnerships%20by%20using%20data%20as%20the%20starting%20point%20for%20better%20collaboration%2C%26quot%3B%20Copeland%20said.%20%26quot%3BWorking%20with%20robots%20actually%20makes%20humans%20listen%20to%20each%20other%20more.%20It's%20ironic%2C%20but%20it%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204729f24-a872-47a2-a12e-cb68228d34bb%5C%22%3EMonevate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMonevate's%20motto%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20focus%20on%20one%20thing%20and%20do%20it%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20focuses%20on%20pricing%20strategy%20for%20software-as-a-service%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20high-growth%20tech%20companies.%20It%20also%20works%20with%20private%20equity%20firms%20to%20assess%20the%20commercial%20viability%20of%20potential%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20James%20Wilton%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20McKinsey%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhighest-paying-boutique-consulting-firms-undergrads-2021-10%238-kearney-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKearney%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhighest-paying-boutique-consulting-firms-undergrads-2021-10%237-zs-associates-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZS%20Associates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founded%20Monevate%20in%202021.%20Wilton%20now%20serves%20as%20the%20Firm's%20managing%20partner.%20The%20firm%20has%2016%20full-time%20consultants%20and%20has%20helped%20over%2050%20SaaS%2C%20tech%2C%20and%20AI%20companies%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20our%20clients%20are%20backed%20by%20venture%20capital%20or%20private%20equity%2C%20and%20increasingly%2C%20we're%20working%20with%20teams%20building%20AI%20products%20and%20features%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilton%20told%20BI%20by%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilton%20said%20clients%20usually%20turn%20to%20Monevate%20when%20they've%20hit%20a%20wall%20with%20their%20current%20strategy%20because%20their%20product%20has%20changed%20or%20the%20market%20has%20evolved.%20%26quot%3BWe%20design%20and%20implement%20fully-baked%20pricing%20strategies%2C%20including%20packaging%2C%20price%20architecture%2C%20and%20price%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilton%20said%20the%20impetus%20to%20launch%20the%20firm%20came%20from%20the%20gaps%20he%20saw%20in%20traditional%20consulting.%20%26quot%3BClients%20often%20complained%20about%20recommendations%20that%20never%20went%20anywhere%2C%20high%20fees%20that%20only%20the%20largest%20companies%20could%20afford%2C%20no%20skin%20in%20the%20game%2C%20inflexible%20delivery%20models%2C%20and%20highly%20variable%20service%20quality%20depending%20on%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonevate%20keeps%20its%20focus%20narrow%2C%20but%20that's%20allowed%20even%20its%20most%20junior%20consultants%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20pricing%20experts%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20firm's%20work%20is%20%26quot%3Bnarrow%20by%20consulting%20standards%2C%20and%20it%20means%20walking%20away%20from%20other%20kinds%20of%20work%2C%20but%20it%20allows%20us%20to%20be%20truly%20great%20at%20what%20we%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bbaba84-9115-4049-905b-9a06d5c8f6d9%5C%22%3EKeystone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeystone%20is%20a%20strategy%20consulting%20firm%20that%20advises%20technology%20companies%2C%20life%20science%20companies%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20law%20firms.%20Its%20clients%20include%20major%20corporations%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20Oracle%2C%20Intel%2C%20Novartis%2C%20and%20Pfizer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20was%20founded%20in%202003%20by%20Greg%20Richards%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20by%20training%20and%20an%20alum%20of%20Microsoft%20and%20Hewlett-Packard%2C%20who%20now%20serves%20as%20an%20advisor%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-business-school-students-launch-class-backed-vc-fund-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Business%20School%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Marco%20Iansiti%2C%20a%20physicist%20and%20professor%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIansiti%20told%20BI%20that%20Keystone%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20%26quot%3Bgeeky%20and%20nerdy%26quot%3B%20than%20traditional%20consulting%20firms.%20%26quot%3BWe%20love%20to%20kind%20of%20get%20deep%20on%20the%20tech%20side%20of%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20team%20includes%20data%20scientists%2C%20AI%20experts%2C%20and%20academics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20consulting%20firms%20are%20embracing%20generative%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20often%20used%20to%20automate%20day-to-day%20work%20like%20writing%20emails%20or%20reviewing%20documents%20and%20contracts%2C%20Iansiti%20said%20Keystone%20is%20focusing%20more%20on%20operational%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOperational%20AI%20is%20used%20to%20transform%20core%20business%20functions%20like%20managing%20supply%20chains%2C%20inventory%2C%20pricing%2C%20and%20forecasting.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20firm%20launched%20%26quot%3BCoreAI%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20team%20dedicated%20to%20using%20AI%20to%20automate%20and%20improve%20these%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20get%20excited%20about%20the%20term%20deep%20enterprise%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Iansiti%20said.%20%26quot%3BDeep%20enterprise%20is%20really%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20deep%20learning%20models%20that%20are%20embedded%20around%20crucial%20operating%20processes%20in%20the%20enterprise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20%26quot%3Bvalue%20add%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20lies%20in%20building%20this%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20unique%20operational%20AI%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243c15cc7-5cf7-4ea8-a813-7d2750dea66e%5C%22%3EFusion%20Collective%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFusion%20Collective%20is%20an%20IT%20consulting%20firm%20that%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20consulting%20services%20to%20clients%2C%20including%20strategy%20and%20management%20advice%2C%20cloud%20transformation%2C%20and%20AI%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20was%20founded%20by%20Blake%20Crawford%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20enterprise%20architecture%20at%20MTV%20Networks%20and%20Viacom%2C%20and%20Yvette%20Schmitter%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20Deloitte%2C%20PwC%2C%20and%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20where%20she%20led%20three%20cloud%20migrations%2C%20including%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20company's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmitter%20said%20that%20in%20her%20experience%2C%20clients%20are%20seeking%20AI%20advice%20from%20consulting%20firms%20before%20they're%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20organizations%20who%20are%20running%20at%2099%20miles%20an%20hour%2C%20hiring%20these%20firms%20to%20build%20these%20AI%20strategy%20documents%2C%20165%20pages%20of%20beautiful%20PowerPoints%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20But%20these%20companies%20still%20can't%20%26quot%3Boperationalize%26quot%3B%20AI%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%3F%20Because%20the%20basic%20infrastructure%20isn't%20there.%20Any%20type%20of%20vulnerability%20that%20they%20have%20in%20security%2C%20their%20cloud%20infrastructure%2C%20is%20just%20exacerbated%20by%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20clients%20chose%20consultants%20based%20on%20trust%2C%20their%20networks%2C%20and%20existing%20business%20relationships%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20believe%20that%20a%20true%20partner%20is%20one%20who's%20going%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20truth.%20Tell%20it%20like%20it%20is%20even%20if%20it%20hurts%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Schmitter%20said.%20To%20that%20end%2C%20she%20said%20she%20asks%20clients%20who%20come%20to%20her%20about%20AI%20strategy%20to%20have%20a%20solid%20grasp%20of%20their%20infrastructure%20footprint%2C%20data%20governance%20policies%2C%20and%20security%20before%20they%20accelerate%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20Fusion%20Collective%20likes%20to%20keep%20its%20advice%20real.%20%26quot%3BIf%20companies%20have%20not%20mastered%20the%20fundamentals%2C%20you're%20not%20ready%20for%20AI%2C%20and%20you're%20not%20ready%20for%20an%20army%20of%20consultants%20to%20come%20in%20to%20do%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmitter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd4ff9a8-fa1d-4c93-a8b5-6bdbdef3a666%5C%22%3ESlideworks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESlideworks%20isn't%20necessarily%20going%20after%20consulting%20firms'%20business%2C%20though%20it%20focuses%20on%20something%20many%20of%20the%20big%20guys%20are%20known%20for%3A%20making%20powerful%20slides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlideworks%20offers%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bhigh-end%26quot%3B%20PowerPoint%20templates%20and%20%26quot%3Btoolkits%26quot%3B%20created%20by%20former%20consultants%20for%20Bain%2C%20BCG%2C%20and%20McKinsey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20work%20as%20a%20consultant%20at%20a%20top-tier%20firm%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20are%20schooled%20every%20day%20in%20best%20practice%20presentations%20and%20slide%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20says%20on%20its%20website.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20offer%20access%20to%20a%20library%20of%20slides%20and%20spreadsheets%20for%20areas%20including%20strategy%2C%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20transformation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20February%20blog%20post%2C%20Alexandra%20Hazard%20Kampmann%2C%20a%20Slideworks%20partner%2C%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bmanagement%20consultants%20are%20often%20made%20fun%20of%20as%20'slide%20monkeys.'%26quot%3B%20Yet%2C%20she%20added%2C%20the%20slide%20is%20a%20%26quot%3