Rubeena%20continues%20to%20sit%20quietly%20on%20her%20wooden%20cot%2C%20processing%20the%20trauma.%20Her%20rabbit%20is%20gone.%20Her%20routine%20was%20shattered.%20But%20her%20spirit%2C%20like%20the%20valley%20she%20calls%20home%2C%20endures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20does%20her%20hope.%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20want%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20softly.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20people%20to%20come%20back%20to%20these%20mountains.%20Not%20in%20fear%E2%80%94but%20with%20smiles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkashmirtimes.com%2Fnews%2Frabbit-girl-of-pahalgam-becomes-lifeline-for-tourists%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20728px)%20100vw%2C%20728px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FHeading-1-1745583669.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FHeading-1-1745583669.png%20728w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FHeading-1-1745583669-300x37.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FHeading-1-1745583669-500x62.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FHeading-1-1745583669-150x19.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-423118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2290%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745586351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fkashmirtimes_2025-04-23_5ubucacr_Rubeena-stands-beside-a-tourist-on-horse-back-1745584282.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D423093%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20tragedy%20struck%20Pahalgam%2C%2016-year-old%20Rubeena%20%E2%80%94%20lovingly%20called%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Rabbit%20Girl%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20opened%20her%20heart%20and%20home%20to%20frighten