l%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20petroleum-derived%20materials%20contribute%20significantly%20to%20pollution%2C%20with%20decomposition%20periods%20extending%20up%20to%20700%20years.%20As%20plastics%20degrade%2C%20they%20fragment%20into%20microplastics%20and%20nanoplastics%2C%20infiltrating%20ecosystems%20and%20raising%20severe%20health%20concerns%2C%20including%20cancer%20and%20reproductive%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Preetam%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20challenges%2C%20Dr%20Preetam%E2%80%99s%20team%20chose%20an%20unconventional%20path%3A%20valorising%20agricultural%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20materials%20selected%20are%20starches%20obtained%20from%20the%20seeds%20of%20jackfruit%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejamun%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20blueberry)%2C%20and%20litchi%2C%20coupled%20with%20tamarind%20kernel%20polysaccharides%20(complex%20carbohydrates)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20underutilised%20byproducts%20harbour%20promising%20potential%20for%20creating%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352330%2Fbubble-wrap-replacement-in-india-coconut-coir-sustainable-packaging-startup-seaweed-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20eco-friendly%20packaging%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Explaining%20further%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CJackfruit%20seeds%2C%20typically%20cast%20aside%20after%20a%20hearty%20feast%2C%20are%20abundant%20in%20starch%20%E2%80%94%20a%20natural%20polymer%20that%2C%20when%20processed%2C%20forms%20a%20robust%20base%20for%20biodegradable%20films.%20Similarly%2C%20jamun%20seeds%20bring%20their%20own%20unique%20properties%20to%20the%20fore.%20Litchi%20seeds%2C%20although%20p